events.name: Rutgers Scarlet Knights at Purdue Boilermakers

headlines.description: — Zach Edey scored 25 points on near-perfect shooting, Camden Heide added a career-high 18 and No. 3 Purdue routed Rutgers 96-68 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Zach Edey scores 25 points on near-perfect shooting, No. 3 Purdue routs Rutgers 96-68

events.name: Washington State Cougars at Arizona Wildcats

headlines.description: — Jaylen Wells hit one of the biggest shots in recent Washington State history to lead the program to a thrilling road victory.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jaylen Wells has late 4-point play to help No. 21 Washington State beat No. 4 Arizona 77-74

video.headline: Washington State takes late lead on 4-point play
